This is Rachel a nord from Riverwood.

These are the mods you need to get the same preset i have:

SG Female Textures Renewal https://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?
Brows https://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?
KS Hairdos HDT https://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70363/?
Citrus Heads https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58989/
Frecklemania https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841

Extra mods used in screenshots:

The Lily - Armour Mashup https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71843/
Bleak ENB https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24828

At this time, i will not be making a follower version of this preset. If any of you wanna take a stab at it, you can do it. Just let me know, thats all i ask.
